graph LR
    RHODS[RHODS Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies (Required/Conditional)
    RHODS -->|platform| OCP[OpenShift Container Platform 4.12+<br/>REQUIRED]
    RHODS -->|traffic mgmt<br/>KServe single-model| Istio[Istio Service Mesh 2.4+<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    RHODS -.->|monitoring| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHODS -.->|certificates| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    RHODS -.->|workflows| ArgoCD[OpenShift GitOps/ArgoCD<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Kubernetes API Integration
    RHODS -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    RHODS -->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Components (Managed)
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web Console]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Jupyter Notebooks]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| KServe[KServe<br/>Model Serving]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Multi-Model Runtime]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Kubeflow Pipelines v2]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| CodeFlare[CodeFlare<br/>Distributed Compute]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Ray[KubeRay<br/>Ray Clusters]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job Scheduling]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>Model Explainability]

    %% Component Integrations
    KServe -->|uses| Istio
    KServe -->|autoscaling| Knative[Knative Serving<br/>Serverless Platform]
    Dashboard -->|auth| OAuth
    Pipelines -->|workflows| ArgoCD

    %% External Services
    RHODS -->|pull images| Registry[Image Registries<br/>registry.redhat.io, quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    RHODS -.->|fetch manifests<br/>devFlags mode| Git[Git Repositories<br/>github.com, gitlab.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Monitoring Integration
    RHODS -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>redhat-ods-monitoring<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
    Prometheus -->|federation| OSMonitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Integration Points (reverse dependencies)
    Dashboard -.->|UI mgmt| RHODS
    Pipelines -.->|component status| RHODS

